episodes.title: A "Fake" Jesus Christ Invited Me Over to His House
episodes.description:
✅  Don't forget to SUBSCRIBE to my channel by clicking here ➞   https://www.youtube.com/@MoreTravelsWithDrewBinsky

▶️ Watch my favorite videos ➞ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zMLHoHf4VWU&list=PLv8sTdl47iyDHwD2MPKeGlJo3rzP7pfr1

Somewhere in rural Kenya, I met a man who claims to be THE REAL Jesus Christ (and millions of poeple in Kenya think it's true). I spent an entire day with Jesus, asking him questions, meeting his followers and really trying to get a grasp on his life. Little did I know that Jesus himself would invite me over to his house for dinner! Here is the full story and experience :)

Follow @MoreTravelsWithDrewBinsky  for more stories from EVERY country, and join me on https://instagram.com/drewbinsky

Watch the documentary that I made about Jesus Christ and his cult here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ejwj5atUxF4

Follow my travels on Instagram! https://instagram.com/drewbinsky

WHO AM I? 
My name is Drew Binsky and I've been to all 197 countries in the world.  I make travel videos about people, culture, and anything else I find interesting on the road.  My ultimate goal is to inspire you to travel far and wide because our planet is beautiful!
